{"tid":1375121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發728文宣助攻] 日文版７２１上環最恐怖１分鐘半片段上線啦！","createTime":"2019-07-28T03:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:04:02.000Z","uid":1806,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3e7540badf8e950ff7b114b531b58175e7d30c","tid":1375121,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:34:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DCPyeQlAUGA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDCPyeQlAUGA&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=2da75e84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DCPyeQlAUGA</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>首先，多謝各位巴絲係上一套文宣片支持同埋意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前已經成功發放左中文版同英文版，今次到日文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[中文版]</span><br />\n721終極文宣片：等我用2分半鐘去話俾大家知721去唔去 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335689</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[英文版]</span><br />\n大穫到咁無外國人知? 我要將７２１上環最恐怖１分鐘半片段流出到國際 !!!! - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355026</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">日本對香港今次運動好留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我哋日文版已經翻譯好啦!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次就要段片流出到日本!!俾我地用分半鐘話俾佢地聽721上環發生左咩事，我哋今日728其中一個目的就係追究返班黑警721既所作所為。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請share俾身邊既日本朋友。唔該晒各位巴絲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.28 追究上環開槍責任</span><br />\n堅持五大訴求 拒絕警黑勾結<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日遮打花園見</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力 齊上齊落<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 不譴責 不撤不散</span></strong></div></span>"},{"pid":"d427d442f718c8e8ec3f01981d8e8d273a5e41b4","tid":1375121,"uid":1806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:36:57.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Credit 俾返Design 文宣圖既巴絲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2Ezqe7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2Ezqe7.png&h=e8b27376&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQNQH1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQNQH1N.png&h=9e4fd553&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tboXn1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtboXn1N.png&h=e7871018&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4HLrgmO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4HLrgmO.png&h=805a8d57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ftxk5e8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFtxk5e8.png&h=74a035ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc727b40efe87e99a45627f14afa03d1ad28eeb9","tid":1375121,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/