or: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">7.28  中上環 下午3點 遮打花園<br />\n捍衛自由 不徹不散<br />\n五大訴求</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選"},{"pid":"44eeda951e895fd6a828af54f62686bf60ef33f3","tid":1375121,"uid":256345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:44:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7321a46105e6bbfb50bcd58bdecd430e8e64381b","tid":1375121,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e9db59a3ee26f851d0b4c734137d7f9faf5dce","tid":1375121,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"228bc3acf9fc802a4ab19ba7d971715ef0cc08d8","tid":1375121,"uid":276514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:37:35.000Z","msg":"[懶人包] 國際大新聞: 示威者發現一輛內有武器既車，懷疑車主為中聯辦官員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374386</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nYIP FOO架車入面...係咩文字...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1374201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1374201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［突發］今次仲鋤你唔死？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1373850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1373850</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n解放軍帽車 車主地址係 南邊圍3里 9號 G/F<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n急，快將葉虎單嘢推畀外媒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372942\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372942</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"r